 * 0: A vehicle, not the classname <OBJECT>
 *
 * Return Value:
 * The selections without hitpoints, i.e. reflectors. <ARRAY>
 *
 * Example:
 * [car] call ace_common_fnc_getSelectionsWithoutHitPoints
 *
 * Public: No
 */

